ษอออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออป
บ      The Three Golden Rules of Poetry                                   บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ  When you're depressed, write poetry!                                   บ
บ  When you're happy, write poetry!                                       บ
บ  When you're hungry, write poetry!                                      บ
บ  When you're ready to puke, write poetry!                               บ
บ  When you're exhausted, write poetry!                                   บ
บ  When you're really up, write poetry!                                   บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ  Write poetry because the landlord is about to evict you from           บ
บ    your apartment.                                                     บ
บ  Write poetry because the world is gonna end tomorrow.                  บ
บ  Write poetry because you used to be a fifteen-year-old kid with        บ
บ   a red guitar in the park.                                             บ
บ  Write poetry because the tests turned out positive.                    บ
บ  Write poetry because you are the Chosen One.                           บ
บ  Write poetry because you didn't get invited to any Halloween parties.  บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ  Write poetry 'cause it's Spring.                                       บ
บ  Write poetry 'cause it's Summer.                                       บ
บ  Write poetry 'cause it's Fall.                                         บ
บ  Write poetry 'cause the soup's too hot.                                บ
บ                                                                         บ
บ  Write poetry 'cause it's good for you!                                 บ
บ  Write poetry 'cause it's bad for you!                                  บ
บ  Write poetry 'cause it makes you crazy!                                บ
บ  Write poetry 'cause it makes you sane!                                 บ
บ  Write poetry 'cause it's the fushia expletive-deleted archenstone      บ
บ  traffic-light angel-hair canvas-bag alpine-horn story of Christmas!    บ
บ  Write poetry!!!                                                        บ
บ  (Or don't, what do I care?)                                            บ
บ                                                                         บ
